<h1>
The Abjad tempo token
</h1>

<p>
All Abjad components afford tempo assignment.

<div class="example-code">
<pre>
   abjad> note = Note(0, (1, 4))
   abjad> note.tempo = ((3, 8), 52)
   hide> measure = Measure((1, 4), [note])
   hide> measure.meter.transparent = True
   hide> show(measure)
</pre>
</div>

<p>
Abjad defines the <strong>tempo token</strong> equal to the pair of a <a href="../duration_token/index.html">duration token</a> and any integer or float interpretable as a metronome marking.

<p>
Examples in the documentation that ask for valid tempo token input accept pairs of the form shown here.
